## Syntax highlighting for emails.

syntax email "\.eml$"

# Quoted lines.
color #AD9 "^>.*"
color #8DC "^> ?>.*"
color #EC9 "^> ?> ?>.*"

# Email addresses.
color #C9E "<[^@]+@[^@]+>"

# URLs.
color #8AE "(https?|ftp)://\S+\.\S+[^[:space:].)]"

# Signatures, even quoted ones.
color #EC9 start="^>* ?-- $" end="^>* ?$"
